==Bio==
"I make all sorts of videos – from documentary through to animation – but I have a focus on using, explaining and promoting Free/Libre/Open Source Software, Free Culture, Open Knowledge and Open Source Hardware.
In 2012/13 I lived a [[Year of Open Source]], I’m part of the [http://openitagency.eu/ Open It Agency] and the [[Open Source Circular Economy Days]] team, and I also run post-production workshops with free software!"

''&mdash; from [http://www.cameralibre.cc/ Camera Libre] main page, 2017''

